{"tid":2379142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲少年刑毀優品360店罪成還押候判 官斥行為「搞破壞、冇成本」「唔知不滿啲乜」","createTime":"2021-01-25T04:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T20:01:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d58b14db1832f350e0d56e086d19a0835563ee","tid":2379142,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13179&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=80068bcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13179</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第三庭 #少年法庭 #庭外消息<br />\n#水佳麗裁判官 <br />\n#20200224天水圍 #裁決<br />\n#刑事損壞<br />\n<br />\nD2: 15歲手足<br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事毀壞<br />\n被控於2020年2月24日在天水圍天耀商場優品360損壞屬於彩鷗國際有限公司的財產。<br />\n<br />\n背景：涉案商店優品360由福建幫林子峰開設，福建幫涉多宗襲擊市民事件，惡名昭著。案發時年僅14歲的本案D1早前承認3項刑事毀壞罪，分別於去年2月1日及2日破壞天水圍置富嘉湖二期優品360，及於同月24日破壞天耀優品360，去年11月13日被判入勞教中心。<br />\n<br />\n速報：罪名成立‼️<br />\n（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年2月5日0930在屯門少年法庭判刑，以待索取感化、社會服務令、勞教中心及更生中心報告<br />\n🛑期間還押候判🛑"},{"pid":"c7f8b21334148de5bca741c309dd587c8af302a9","tid":2379142,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"天水圍2間「優品360」去年2月3度遭人破壞，警方其後截獲2名少年，其中14歲少年早前承認3項刑事毀壞罪被判入勞教中心。另1名14歲少年否認1項刑毀罪受審後，裁判官水佳麗今早在屯門裁判法院指被告鞋子、背囊中搜出衣物及身形與店內閉路電視所見相符，加上被告證供混亂全不接納，故裁定被告刑事毀壞罪成。辯方求情指被告自小罹患自閉症、腦癲癇及抑鬱症，成長過程具挑戰。水官訓斥被告行為「只係搞破壞，冇成本」，「唔知不滿啲乜」，押後判刑至下月5日早上，期間索取感化、社會服務令、更生中心及勞教中心報告，被告須還押看管。<br />\n<br />\n水官裁決時指被毀店舖閉路電視片段可見第2名入內破壞的疑犯身形略胖，穿部份黑色衣著，鞋帶白邊，鞋呈白色山形圖案。其後被告偕已認罪的同案少年被告於洪福邨被截停時，雖然身穿藍色外套，惟其背囊中被搜出黑色外套，手袖帶白點，背囊中間有橫條印有字樣，加上灰色3M手套及其身形，均與案發時疑犯特徵相符。被告供稱背囊屬另一少年，因其指背囊太重，交予被告手持，水官認為被告解釋不值得相信，因背囊中僅得普通衣物，不會太重。<br />\n<br />\n水官形容被告證供混亂，被告先供稱下午1時從天耀家中出發乘輕鐵，半小時後到洪水橋吃午飯，然而又指在新北江商場會合同案少年，故折返樂湖站，再去洪水橋。被告供稱3時相約友人在洪水橋打籃球，2人2時45分於洪水橋被截停時卻正打算進入食肆用膳，而未有通知相約的友人。水官批評被告行程「走來走去，不見得合理」，「3點打波一啲都唔覺得真實」。被告談到與警員對答過程又反覆不一，稱替同伴持背囊卻又「自把自為」打開察看，警員查問下又不表明不屬自己所有，又不斷用不同理由解釋為何沒有看見警員搜查背囊。水官認為被告不可信可靠，供詞全不接納，亦反駁辯方指被告醫療報告意見反映病情進度良好，法庭上對答感覺不到被告自閉或智力有問題，斷言被告作供在「講大話」，遂裁定被告罪成。<br />\n<br />\n辯方呈上3封其家人、訓導主任及信義會外展社工求情信，指被告乖巧孝順，為人內向單純，自小罹患自閉症、抑鬱症及腦癲癇症，學業成績不佳，沒有朋友同學，一直讀到小六也並不開心，需輔導協助，至進入特殊中學才能認識同學，會相約一起做運動。辯方又指被告平易近人，樂於助人，主動幫助興趣班同學，防疫時派發物資，未來希望成為咖啡師。辯方最後指被告願意賠償控方要求的527元，犯案時間短，破壞不算嚴重，而被告成長飽受挑戰，希望法庭索取感化報告等量刑作全面考慮。<br />\n<br />\n水官語重心長勸誡被告「你要記住，好多人開舖頭做生意係要好多努力⋯⋯要花好多心思，你只係搞破壞，破壞冇成本，手一揮架一掃」，「你必須要學到教訓，可能好多人清楚個動機，我唔知不滿啲乜，以莫須有罪名，引來自己村居民不便，希望你自己反省下啱定唔啱」，遂按辯方要求索取報告以量刑。"},{"pid":"f3c31b985c6d611ee990a6cfccbe8e70421cc52b","tid":2379142,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"水官變了"},{"pid":"61132cc91b1383dfdca505f17c34a5baa6cdc431","tid":2379142,"uid":112581,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"f3c31b985c6d611ee990a6cfccbe8e70421cc52b","tid":2379142,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"水官變了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"冇變過<br />\n係有人岳黃成癮<br />\n根本冇一隻狗官係無辜"},{"pid":"3ecba48566d5501a25fce0ab2625d0e6d2568ce3","tid":2379142,"uid":115579,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"f3c31b985c6d611ee990a6cfccbe8e70421cc52b","tid":2379142,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"水官變了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"其實本身佢都係咁上下，只係其他狗官太出色"},{"pid":"6c382e88bbca35624191de1b40fb1e4414dbe4e8","tid":2379142,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"e732692f58e1de487321180120b51b7694db17ad","tid":2379142,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"勞教中心....惨"},{"pid":"25af0b5ae1a3a99222e3d3672f406a7439c55fd5","tid":2379142,"uid":239842,"like":10,"dislike":25,"score":-15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"咁佢又錯唔晒。<br />\n真係唔知為咩。<br />\n打爛間鋪唔知對政權有咩影響同不滿。<br />\n<br />\n利申五毛"},{"pid":"2a3151e571b37318b1650f7a5f07dfe6f6f9d39e","tid":2379142,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ecba48566d5501a25fce0ab2625d0e6d2568ce3","tid":2379142,"uid":115579,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"f3c31b985c6d611ee990a6cfccbe8e70421cc52b","tid":2379142,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"水官變了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"其實本身佢都係咁上下，只係其他狗官太出色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"係，水狗不嬲都係紅官，只不過係依家要追落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5ba77f868a7411411308db8b82512bd3622823","tid":2379142,"uid":92,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/img.erogazopple.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4-9.gif?resize=360%2C206\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fimg.erogazopple.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F4-9.gif%3Fresize%3D360%252C206&h=26dec484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11ec20c6ffece1cd70e2ec7e6775952c78858307","tid":2379142,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"又係水佳麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55bab3e1cfaa41cb99b877aab7c1779c83e2edf","tid":2379142,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"水官應該有機會判感化/短小時社會服務令"},{"pid":"5554b866a922369b9988095c069db54dc7cc9f37","tid":2379142,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d219de38d9bf6aae447c460bf79c5d032d97db4","tid":2379142,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f3c31b985c6d611ee990a6cfccbe8e70421cc52b","tid":2379142,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"水官變了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b3ac7b632e3d19d020067059e9484ad00416d3","tid":2379142,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55bab3e1cfaa41cb99b877aab7c1779c83e2edf","tid":2379142,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"水官應該有機會判感化/短小時社會服務令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"應該唔會<br />\n佢之前俾高院話過判得太輕<br />\n而家應該會偏向判重啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c14a39e485d9a68b8b0d675d4609f0571db3845","tid":2379142,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"又比人水左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出左事比人割晒"},{"pid":"dfb79ddf2b43c9f88cdcc24f73476d601ae5d003","tid":2379142,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc769221a997d77205c101928b6203885b0fab89","tid":2379142,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"水官語重心長勸誡被告「你要記住，好多人開舖頭做生意係要好多努力⋯⋯要花好多心思，你只係搞破壞，破壞冇成本，手一揮架一掃」，「你必須要學到教訓，可能好多人清楚個動機，我唔知不滿啲乜，以莫須有罪名，引來自己村居民不便，希望你自己反省下啱定唔啱」<br />\n<br />\n全文都唔係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3658bf42aa019b2989f389ff82feec16d7007f5","tid":2379142,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"兩名14歲少年去年涉「裝修」被指為藍店的優品360分店，推倒貨架貨品及收銀機，被控刑事毀壞罪。其中一人早前認罪，另一人受審，裁判官今裁決指，憑被告身型及波鞋樣式，認定他便是閉路電視拍到破壞店舖的人，並指其自辯供稱約了朋友打籃球的說法不可信，裁定罪成，還柙至下周五（24日）判刑。裁判官向少年直言，做生意需要很多努力，少年所為卻只是搞破壞，「破壞係冇成本，隻手一掃，破壞完畢」，並謂針對個別店舖的破壞屬於莫須有，亦引起居民不便。<br />\n<br />\n被告被控去年2月24日下午在天水圍天耀商場內的優品360犯案。他其後在區內被截查，警員未待他的家人到場便查問及警誡，聲稱以免被告有時間「作故仔」。辯方在審訊時，爭議指被告對警方作出的招認屬非自願作出，惟法庭最終接納招認口供呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n警查問與案無關事情 官指不合理<br />\n<br />\n裁判官水佳麗今在屯門法院裁決，先交代接納招認的理由，直指警員23353陳加林在被告父母不在場下，查問與本案無關、在另外兩天發生的事情，屬不合理，亦不見得查問有逼切性；但警員查問被告當天去過何處及曾與甚麼人一起，則屬公平合理，亦符合當局相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/L5OLTHDBERHJJPKRLFE5YZD2H4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FL5OLTHDBERHJJPKRLFE5YZD2H4%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=7041561f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FL5OLTHDBERHJJPKRLFE5YZD2H4%2F&h=f1b9aa61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/L5OLTHDBERHJJPKRLFE5YZD2H4/</a>"},{"pid":"81ff33554d8a69bc4ef0f9762081183e17efa38a","tid":2379142,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55bab3e1cfaa41cb99b877aab7c1779c83e2edf","tid":2379142,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"水官應該有機會判感化/短小時社會服務令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"佢本身已經喺勞教"},{"pid":"917300aa94900ce22610cdd3530aa2554293a3f5","tid":2379142,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6874e7cc0829711236f2e4116361a784f5ee3e3","tid":2379142,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca215b191ddc017aef84449278696a081c6c061","tid":2379142,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c498342accd274f0dbc8a4685ec741dea9382ce","tid":2379142,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b309538c0a07e535e6c2465d0e35a3c12fb6aec4","tid":2379142,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"啲官太離地，以為香港人抗爭係純粹搞破壞"}]}